{"tid":2176932,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"全民檢測設網頁 資料欠奉","createTime":"2020-08-27T11:14:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-27T11:14:03.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1cbffb400fcb383b1e4875e9648649d32c7bc5ca","tid":2176932,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T11:14:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200827/PNTOORAK4BBEBASHHCMGKQIIBM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200827%2FPNTOORAK4BBEBASHHCMGKQIIBM%2F&d=a8feNXbjtso6d%2BC97Zvpk7Tr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=775f8d75\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200827%2FPNTOORAK4BBEBASHHCMGKQIIBM%2F&h=99df108b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200827/PNTOORAK4BBEBASHHCMGKQIIBM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n全民檢測設網頁 資料欠奉<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/zD_MrbWEFOzonIDGV4OiWuzdjR8=/1775x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DFKS65LNFRGDXME6ILFELEYPB4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FzD_MrbWEFOzonIDGV4OiWuzdjR8%3D%2F1775x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDFKS65LNFRGDXME6ILFELEYPB4.jpg&h=1dbb53cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■政府推動全民病毒檢測，但至今未有地點等細節；圖為政府為外傭採樣化驗。 中通社<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】全民檢測將下周二展開，政府延至昨天才設立網頁簡介檢測計劃，但各區檢測中心地點、具體採樣流程等資料仍未公佈。協助招募檢測人手的醫學界人指出，目前新界東及新界西的檢測中心仍然人手不足，政府亦不夠時間為所有檢測人員進行N95口罩的面型配合測試。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新界檢測中心仍缺人手<br />\n<br />\n據普及社區檢測計劃的網頁公佈，市民可由本周六起於網上預約參與檢測，程序包括輸入姓名、身份證號碼及手提電語號碼，並選擇社區檢測中心及時段。完成預約後，手機將收到。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n醫學界前晚曾與政府會面，了解檢測計劃運作程序。西醫工會會長楊超發表示。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/3yJ8ZiS7RPSmTrH6DB2V5cZkqgs=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YZ5LSAZSCFGY7EAUVKFPKMG5EM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F3yJ8ZiS7RPSmTrH6DB2V5cZkqgs%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYZ5LSAZSCFGY7EAUVKFPKMG5EM.jpg&h=45a1ca64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■陳松青昨到中山紀念公園體育館視察臨時氣膜實驗室，稱實驗室已準備就緒。<br />\n<br />\n楊超發又引述政府表示，18區檢測中心全部都是室內，包括學校禮堂及社區會堂等。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n醫學會會長蔡堅表示，政府稱沒有足夠時間及人手為所有參與計劃的醫護人員完成。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n而特區政府檢測工作組（工作組）組長陳松青，昨聯同內地支援隊隊長余德文。。。。。。"}]}